title: Learning Rock and Roll Piano taught by Bob Hoban [1991, DVD5, EN
description:
Homespun - Learning Rock and Roll Piano taught by Bob Hoban [1991, DVD5, ENG]




Here are the great '50s and '60s rock 'n' roll piano styles made popular by Jerry Lee Lewis and Fats Domino! Bob Hoban makes it easy to learn how to do slides, rolls, melodic figures, rhythm patterns, shuffles, right-hand licks, slurs, solos, runs, single-note leads. 'pushed' notes and 'power beginnings'
